title: Tick, Tick, Talk, 2019 Recession Coming
text: I'm now predicting a 2019 recession as the major economic news for this year (both US and global).

title: Booming jobs market is leaving the retail industry behind
text: Since 2017, retail has lost more than 140,000 jobs; the sector added to those losses in March 2019 with a loss of more than 11,000.

title: Huawei P30 Pro Hands-On Review: Superpower Camera Lenses
text: The Huawei P30 Pro’s camera is like having Superman’s eyes. It can see in the dark, and zoom right in on objects much too far away to see clearly otherwise.

title: Davos Debate: How to Avoid "Impact Washing"
